<h3 class="nx-font-semibold nx-tracking-tight nx-text-slate-900 dark:nx-text-slate-100 nx-mt-8 nx-text-2xl">为控制参数添加 GUI 控件<a href="#为控制参数添加-gui-控件" id="为控制参数添加-gui-控件" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section"></a></h3>
