<li class="nx-my-2">在这里，我们更新 <code class="nx-border-black nx-border-opacity-[0.04] nx-bg-opacity-[0.03] nx-bg-black nx-break-words nx-rounded-md nx-border nx-py-0.5 nx-px-[.25em] nx-text-[.9em] dark:nx-border-white/10 dark:nx-bg-white/10" dir="ltr">cube.rotation.x</code> 的值，使得滑块能实时控制立方体的旋转。</li>
